value.description:
About Event

​What does it take to deliver production-ready Voice AI experiences?

​Join Modal and Phonic in an evening thinking about the real-world requirements for Voice AI. Our speakers will cover:

​True Conversational Intelligence — how do build voice agents that guide conversations toward task-driven goals?

​Voice-to Voice Latency — how to build a chatbot fast enough to carry a natural conversation?

​With:

​Ben Shababo, Forward Deployed Engineer & Developer Relations at Modal

​Nikhil
